== Months of Kōgo ==
In a {{ill|Common Era|ja|西暦}} year whose final digit is 1 or 6 (i.e. when the Ten Heavenly Stems are {{ill|Xin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)}} or {{ill|Bing|ja|丙|1=Hinoe (丙)}}), the month of {{ill|May|ja|5月}} becomes the {{ill|Month (Calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|lt=Month}} of Kōgo. However, here the term “month” may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}} or to a seasonal month (from {{ill|Mangzhong|ja|芒種}} until the day before {{ill|Xiaoshu|ja|小暑}}) as applicable.

