== Months of Kōgo ==
In a {{ill|Common Era|ja|西暦|12=draft|12=draft}} year whose final digit is 1 or 6 (i.e. when the Ten Heavenly Stems are {{ill|Xin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|12=draft|12=draft}} or {{ill|Bing|ja|丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|12=draft|12=draft}}), the month of {{ill|May|ja|5月|12=draft|12=draft}} becomes the {{ill|Month (Calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|lt=Month|12=draft|12=draft}} of Kōgo. However, here the term “month” may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft}} or to a seasonal month (from {{ill|Mangzhong|ja|芒種|12=draft|12=draft}} until the day before {{ill|Xiaoshu|ja|小暑|12=draft|12=draft}}) as applicable.

== Days of Kōgo ==
The {{ill|Day Selection|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu|12=draft|12=draft}} for a Kōgo day is as follows.
=== Day Selection ===
A Kōgo day is the 2nd day of {{ill|Ten Heaven, One Heaven|ja|天一天上|12=draft|12=draft}}.

