{{infobox Chinese|l=Yang Wood Horse|kanji=甲午|romaji=kinoe uma|onyomi=kōgo|p=jiǎwǔ|w=chia-wu|mi=ʈ͡ʂja̠²¹ u²¹|y=gaap6 ng5|j=gaap6 ng5|ci=kaːp̚ ŋo|mc=kæp ŋo|oc-bs=kaːp ŋaʔ}}
{{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive}}

'''Yang Wood Horse also known as 甲午''' (kinoeuma, kōbokunouma, kougo) is one of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|干支|12=draft|12=draft}}.

It is the 31st combination of the Sexagenary cycle; the preceding combination is {{ill|Guisi|ja|癸巳|12=draft|12=draft}} and the following combination is {{ill|Otsuji|ja|乙未|12=draft|12=draft}}. In the system of {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|陰陽五行思想|lt=Yin-Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=陰陽五行|12=draft|12=draft}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|lt=Ten Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft}}’ {{ill|Jia|ja|甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Wood|ja|木|12=draft|12=draft}}, while the {{ill|Twelve Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|12=draft|12=draft}}’ {{ill|Horse|ja|午|1=Horse (zodiac)|lt=Horse (午)|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Fire|ja|火|12=draft|12=draft}}, and they interact by {{ill|Mutual Generation|ja|五行思想#相生（そうじょう）|lt=Mutual Generation|lt_ja=相生|12=draft|12=draft}} (Wood produces Fire).

== Years of Kōgo ==
A year in the {{ill|Common Era|ja|西暦|12=draft|12=draft}} that leaves a remainder of 34 when divided by 60 is a {{ill|Year|ja|年|12=draft|12=draft}} of Kōgo.
