'''Yang Wood Horse also known as 甲午''' (kinoeuma, kōbokunouma, kougo) is one of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|干支|qq=draft|qq=draft}}.

It is the 31st combination of the Sexagenary cycle; the preceding combination is {{ill|Guisi|ja|癸巳|qq=draft|qq=draft}} and the following combination is {{ill|Otsuji|ja|乙未|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. In the system of {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|陰陽五行思想|lt=Yin-Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=陰陽五行|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|lt=Ten Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft}}’ {{ill|Jia|ja|甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Wood|ja|木|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, while the {{ill|Twelve Earthly Branches|1=Earthly Branches|lt=Twelve Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|qq=draft|qq=draft}}’ {{ill|Horse|ja|午|1=Horse (zodiac)|lt=Horse (午)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Fire|ja|火|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, and they interact by {{ill|Mutual Generation|ja|五行思想#相生（そうじょう）|lt=Mutual Generation|lt_ja=相生|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (Wood produces Fire).

