== Months of Kōgo ==
In a {{ill|Common Era|ja|西暦|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=西暦|4=zh|5=公元|6=es|7=Era común|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} year whose final digit is 1 or 6 (i.e. when the Ten Heavenly Stems are {{ill|Xin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} or {{ill|Bing|ja|丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}), the month of {{ill|May|ja|5月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} becomes the {{ill|Month (Calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|lt=Month|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} of Kōgo. However, here the term “month” may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} or to a seasonal month (from {{ill|Mangzhong|ja|芒種|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} until the day before {{ill|Xiaoshu|ja|小暑|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}) as applicable.

