{{infobox Chinese|l=Yang Wood Horse|kanji=甲午|romaji=kinoe uma|onyomi=kōgo|p=jiǎwǔ|w=chia-wu|mi=ʈ͡ʂja̠²¹ u²¹|y=gaap6 ng5|j=gaap6 ng5|ci=kaːp̚ ŋo|mc=kæp ŋo|oc-bs=kaːp ŋaʔ|qq=}}
{{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=}}

'''Yang Wood Horse also known as 甲午''' (kinoeuma, kōbokunouma, kougo) is one of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|干支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}.

It is the 31st combination of the Sexagenary cycle; the preceding combination is {{ill|Guisi|ja|癸巳|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} and the following combination is {{ill|Otsuji|ja|乙未|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}. In the system of {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|陰陽五行思想|lt=Yin-Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=陰陽五行|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|lt=Ten Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}’ {{ill|Jia|ja|甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Wood|ja|木|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, while the {{ill|Twelve Earthly Branches|1=Earthly Branches|lt=Twelve Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}’ {{ill|Horse|ja|午|1=Horse (zodiac)|lt=Horse (午)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Fire|ja|火|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, and they interact by {{ill|Mutual Generation|ja|五行思想#相生（そうじょう）|lt=Mutual Generation|lt_ja=相生|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (Wood produces Fire).

== Years of Kōgo ==
A year in the {{ill|Common Era|ja|西暦|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=西暦|4=zh|5=公元|6=es|7=Era común|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} that leaves a remainder of 34 when divided by 60 is a {{ill|Year|ja|年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} of Kōgo.
