=== Events ===
* In {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|qq=}} 27th Year (1894 AD) – The {{ill|Kōgo Peasant War|ja|甲午農民戦争|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōgo Peasant War|qq=}} (also known as the Tōgakutō Rebellion) occurred.

== Months of Kōgo ==
In a {{ill|Common Era|ja|西暦|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=西暦|4=zh|5=公元|6=es|7=Era común|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=}} year whose final digit is 1 or 6 (i.e. when the Ten Heavenly Stems are {{ill|Xin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xin|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (辛)|qq=}} or {{ill|Bing|ja|丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bing|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (丙)|qq=}}), the month of {{ill|May|ja|5月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May|qq=}} becomes the {{ill|Month (Calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|lt=Month|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Month (Calendar)|qq=}} of Kōgo. However, here the term “month” may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to a seasonal month (from {{ill|Mangzhong|ja|芒種|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mangzhong|qq=}} until the day before {{ill|Xiaoshu|ja|小暑|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xiaoshu|qq=}}) as applicable.

== Days of Kōgo ==
The {{ill|Day Selection|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Day Selection|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=}} for a Kōgo day is as follows.
=== Day Selection ===
A Kōgo day is the 2nd day of {{ill|Ten Heaven, One Heaven|ja|天一天上|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ten Heaven, One Heaven|qq=}}.

